no anime zone

I AM VERY INTERESTED IN: techno, hardstyle, jumpstyle, hyperpop, any live from earth klub releases

i use lazer 95% of the time and i have also worked on the editor. feel free to send me feedback or things you want

maps i made / collabed on:
  1. Ian - Timeout; unsubmitted nft from years ago that i sent to ent and we decided to rank it
  2. MIMIDEATH - if god didnt want us to snort worms he wouldnt have made them cylindrical!; first actual full mapset
  3. Lil Mariko - Boring; mapping assignment / hitsounding practice
  4. YABUJIN - CHALICE OF MIND; first attempt at taiko
  5. SOPHIE - NOTHING MORE TO SAY; second attempt at taiko]
  6. Vintazh - Eva; storyboarding
  7. Death Grips - Year of the Snitch; my most batshit project ever, maybe i will be comfortable enough to finish this one day
  8. Saint Pepsi - Private Caller; first time using the editor, was originally made in 2018 and mumble wanted to try to finish the map (2nd half)
other maps are probably not worth looking at (including the nft unsubmitted graveyard)

thank you to (in no particular order): Mumble, Ancelysia, ent, nanoya, Dpao, Xarr, Maarvin, OliBomby

you guys are cool and are the reason i started mapping again
